---
id: egg-salad-box
title: Egg Salad Box
description: A meal-prep lunch box with egg salad, bread, and grapes.
servings: 2
mealTypes: [lunch]
tags: [meal-prep, high-protein]
prep time: 15 minutes
cook time: 10 minutes
---

Boil @eggs{4} in a #pot{} for ~eggs{10%minutes}, then cool and chop.

Mix eggs with @Greek yogurt{2%tbsp}, @Dijon mustard{1%tsp}, and @celery stalks{2}(diced) in a #mixing bowl{}.

Pack with @whole grain bread{4%slices} and @grapes{1%cup}.
